attributionInfo.brokerName: S A Moore Realty Services, LLC

data.description: Desert oasis in the heart of Vail w/towering ceilings & walls of windows. Open floorplan w/gourmet Kitchen that flows to spacious great room w/fireplace, & formal dining room. Kitchen features stainless appliances,dual ovens, five-burner gas cooktop, granite counters, breakfast bar & pantry. Primary bedroom offers 2 closets, backyard access, shower w/ pebble floor and rain shower head. All bedrooms are generously sized. Enjoy the best of Tucson's outdoor living: expansive covered patio, built-in BBQ, fire pit,   walled in yard, artificial turf lawn, mountain/desert views, EZ care landscaping  features Ocotillos, Saguaros, cactus specimens & mature trees. Oversized three-car garage offers additional parking and toy storage. Assumable VA Loan at 4.49% interest (need about 100K to close)
